	* cipher/rijndael-vp-aarch64.c: ... here.
	* cipher/rijndael-vp-riscv.c: New.
	* cipher/rijndael-vp-simd128.h: Use '__m128i_const' type for constant
	vector values and use *_amemld() macros to load these values to vector
	registers.
