	+ commit e924ce456d5728a81c148de4a6eb23373cb70ca0
	* cipher/rijndael-aesni.c (aesni_ocb_enc): Remove call to
	'aesni_ocb_checksum', instead perform checksumming inline with offset
	calculations.

