	sized buf_cpy/xor* operations.
	* cipher/camellia-glue.c: Ditto.
	* cipher/cast5.c: Ditto.
	* cipher/cipher-aeswrap.c: Ditto.
	* cipher/cipher-cbc.c: Ditto.
