	'nblocks'.
	(whirlpool_add): Update 'nblocks' instead of 'length', and add early
	return at one spot.
	(whirlpool_write): Check for 'nblocks' overflow.
	(whirlpool_final): Convert 'nblocks' to bit-counter, and use
	whirlpool_write instead of whirlpool_add.

