2013-09-04  Werner Koch  <wk@gnupg.org>

	Change mpicalc to use Libgcrypt and install it.
	+ commit 1d23040b659661b4086c079cb9fd5f37189a7020
	* src/mpicalc.c: Make use of gcry_ functions.
