	(do_encrypt): Disable input/output alignment when USE_ARMV6_ASM.
	(do_decrypt_aligned) [USE_ARMV6_ASM]: Use ARMv6 assembly function.
	(do_decrypt): Disable input/output alignment when USE_ARMV6_ASM.
