	Rename all ChangeLog files to ChangeLog-2011.

2011-12-01  Werner Koch  <wk@gnupg.org>

	NB: Changes done before December 1st, 2011 are described in
	per directory files named ChangeLog-2011.  See doc/HACKING for
	details.

